lead_paragraph: Chile's Claudio Bravo made two excellent first-half saves before coming off injured just past the hour as his side drew 0-0 away to Colombia in a World Cup qualifier in Barranquilla on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Bravo Injured Helping Chile Draw 0-0 in Colombia
